Package org.codeseed.common.config

Primary package for the Code Seed Configuration module.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Configuration
    Empty marker interface for configuration interfaces.
    PropertySource
    Contract of a source of configuration information.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnnotationPropertySource<A extends Annotation>
    A property source whose values are triggered by the presence of an annotation.
    ConfigurationBuilder
    A builder of Configuration instances.
    DefaultValuePropertySource
    A property source which wraps some number of other property sources and falls back to the value in the @DefaultValue annotation.
    PropertySources
    Static utility methods pertaining to PropertySource instances.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    MissingPropertyException
    Thrown from any configuration method whose property value was not defined by any property sources.
    PropertyConversionException
    Thrown when a property cannot be converted.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    DefaultValue
    Provides a default property value.
    EnvironmentVariable
    Used to load a configuration value from an environment variable.
    SystemPreference
    Used to load a configuration value from a system preference.
    SystemProperty
    Used to load a configuration value from a system property.
    UserPreference
    Used to load a configuration value from a user preference.
